channel.title: Source won't go online
channel.description:
Hey guys, need some minor help with my server, this has got me stumped.
I can run any of my source and they will go online, but this one source i have won't go online for some reason.. It like auto connects to local host.
The source i am using is DeathlyPvpz V2.
Would anybody care to help ? Thanks.
